27/06/2008
VAN, Turkey -- Police on Friday (June 27th) seized 208kg of heroin in Van, the capital of the eastern province of the same name.
Two suspects are under arrest, and police are pursuing others.
Authorities found the drugs, distributed in 408 packs, inside a truck travelling from the town of Gurpinar.
(Kathimerini, ANA-MPA, NTV - 27/06/08)
